# Local-only symlink to the legacy content source used by scripts/build-site.mjs
# and scripts/compare-routes.mjs (the parity-comparison harness). Points outside
# the repo (../content_backup) so it must never be committed -- doing so breaks
# `next build` on Vercel with ENOENT, since that directory doesn't exist there.
/content

